    <sec id="SEC2-5">
      <title>Online server construction</title>
      <p>The SRAMP online server was built under the ‘Linux+Apache+Django’ framework. The visualization of the structural context of the predicted m<sup>6</sup>A sites was powered by the VARNA structure visualization tool (<xref rid="B31" ref-type="bibr">31</xref>).</p>
    </sec>
